        |       |                                               |       |        
        |       | blurb:                                        |       |        
        |       |                                               |       |        
        |       | Chronicles of the Deep is the third and last  |       |        
        |       | part of a series of LP&#039;s and CD&#039;s that have   |       |        
        |       | been making a huge impact on the atmospheric  |       |        
        |       | drum & bass scene. The Chronicles its self    |       |        
        |       | tells a story of beautiful strings, great     |       |        
        |       | warriors and mysterious landscapes all        |       |        
        |       | written down by some of the greatest          |       |        
        |       | discoveries made in atmospheric drum & bass.  |       |        
        |       | Not only told by the Usual Suspects, but also |       |        
        |       | displaying great words from the up & coming   |       |        
        |       | talented producers out there.                 |       |        
        |       |                                               |       |        
        |       | This CD is partly a compilation of 10 tunes   |       |        
        |       | originally released on the Chronicles of the  |       |        
        |       | Deep LP. After the LP Fokuz released a Second |       |        
        |       | double pack with 4 extra tracks. Prior to the |       |        
        |       | LP a single with 2 tracks to promote the LP.  |       |        
        |       | Both these other projects where part of the   |       |        
        |       | complete Chronicles series, called Chronicles |       |        
        |       | Sampler, and Chronicles continued, the        |       |        
        |       | aftermath. These 16 tracks are all together   |       |        
        |       | represented on this double CD.                |       |        
        |       |                                               |       |        
        |       | In addition to these 16 tracks you find 9     |       |        
        |       | Exclusive gems which where never released on  |       |        
        |       | vinyl, and will only be available on this CD. |       |        
        |       | This CD is carefully compiled in such a way   |       |        
        |       | that you will experience this whole package   |       |        
        |       | as a complete Journey. A Journey that starts  |       |        
        |       | off deep inside the valleys of Neverland, and |       |        
        |       | slowly works its way up to the mountains      |       |        
        |       | through all types of atmospheres,             |       |        
        |       | encountering hot steamy deserts, huge         |       |        
        |       | tropical rainforests, deep sea oceans and     |       |        
        |       | impressive icy polar surroundings... from the |       |        
        |       | deep and minimalistic dubby vibes to full     |       |        
        |       | happy vocal driven tunes served with heavy    |       |        
        |       | slamming feel good tracks that will get the   |       |        
        |       | dancefloors moving anywhere around the        |       |        
        |       | world.                                        |       |        
        |       |                                               |       |        
        |       | Great philosophers you will meet on the way   |       |        
        |       | are great minds like Zyonbase, CLS & Wax,     |       |        
        |       | Lynx, Spectrasoul, Atlantic Connections, Bcee |       |        
        |       | & Lomax, Mutt, Switch, Naibu, Donnie Dubson,  |       |        
        |       | Stunna, Greeley, Whizz & Daze, Calculon,      |       |        
        |       | Brother and many others.                      |       |        
        |       |                                               |       |
